with our expert recruitment strategies and tools.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Performance Management</h3>\n                    <p>Develop and implement systems that foster employee growth and productivity.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Compensation & Benefits</h3>\n                    <p>Design competitive and compliant compensation packages to attract and retain talent.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Employee Relations</h3>\n                    <p>Navigate complex employee issues with professional guidance and support.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>HR Compliance</h3>\n                    <p>Ensure your organization adheres to all relevant labor laws and regulations.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Training & Development</h3>\n                    <p>Invest in your workforce with tailored training programs for skill enhancement.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" style=\"margin-top: 40px;\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.6;\">\n                HR Solutions Pro is dedicated to empowering businesses with exceptional human resources strategies. We partner with organizations of all sizes to build engaged, productive, and compliant workforces. Our team of experienced HR professionals provides tailored solutions to meet your unique challenges and opportunities.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get a Free Consultation</a>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" style=\"margin-top: 40px;\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: cen